---
layout: base.njk
title: PoliTechs.uk — Politics meets Technology
---
{% from "event-card.njk" import eventCard %}

<main>
  {# Hero #}
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Politics meets Technology.</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Digital technology and AI now shapes how we access media, jobs, healthcare, education, and public services. They connect us, but they can also divide, exploit, and exclude. Yet we rarely stop to ask how we want them to serve people, communities, and democracy.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta d-flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <a href="/events/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Upcoming Events</a>
          <a href="#petition" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">Sign the Pledge</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Mission #}
  <section class="mission-section section-pad">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8">
          <h2 class="section-title text-center">Our Mission</h2>
          <div class="mission-blocks">
            <div class="mission-block">
              <h3 class="mission-label">The Problem</h3>
              <p>
                Politics and technology are shaping each other at speed — yet they operate in silos. Policymakers
                lack technical literacy. Technologists lack civic engagement. The result? Legislation that lags
                reality, tech that erodes democracy, and society left behind.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mission-block">
              <h3 class="mission-label">Our Method</h3>
              <p>
                We connect people from politics and technology — through events,
                conversations, and collaborative projects. We raise the debate on the key issues: 
                digital rights, AI governance, open data, and civic tech.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mission-block">
              <h3 class="mission-label">Our Goal</h3>
              <p>
                A society where technology serves the many, not the few — where democratic values shape the
                digital world, and where our nation leads the way in responsible, human-centred innovation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Upcoming Events #}
  <section class="events-preview-section section-pad bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-4">Upcoming Events</h2>
      <div class="row g-4">
      {% for event in events %}
      {% if loop.index0 < 2 %}
        <div class="col-md-6">
          {{ eventCard(event) }}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/events/" class="btn btn-outline-primary">See all events</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Mailing List #}
  <section class="signup-section section-pad">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6">
          <div class="mailchimp-signup">
            <h4>Stay informed</h4>
            <p>Join our mailing list for event updates, policy briefs, and opportunities to get involved.</p>
            <form action="https://politechs.us1.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=PLACEHOLDER&amp;id=PLACEHOLDER" method="post" target="_blank">
              <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <label for="mce-EMAIL" class="visually-hidden">Email address</label>
                <input type="email" id="mce-EMAIL" name="EMAIL" placeholder="Your email address" required class="form-control flex-grow-1" />
                {# Mailchimp honeypot — replace with actual value from your embed code #}
                <div style="position:absolute;left:-5000px" aria-hidden="true">
                  <input type="text" name="b_PLACEHOLDER_PLACEHOLDER" tabindex="-1" value="" />
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Subscribe</button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Petition #}
  <section id="petition" class="petition-section section-pad bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <h2 class="mb-3">Take Action: Sign the Pledge</h2>
          <p class="petition-text mb-4">
            We're calling for a future where digital is central - and where we have a say in how it evolves. Politics and Technology must work together for society.
          </p>
          <a href="https://nationalconversations.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">
            Sign the Pledge
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
